'''vsftpd''' ('''V'''ery '''S'''ecure '''FTP''' '''D'''aemon) is a major FTP server.

== Installation ==
Install {{Package|net-ftp/vsftpd}}:
{{Emerge|vsftpd}}

== Configuration ==

==== Anonymous access ====
{{RootCmd|mkdir /home/ftp}}

{{File|/etc/vsftpd/vsftpd.conf||<pre>
listen=YES
local_enable=NO
anonymous_enable=YES
write_enable=NO
anon_root=/home/ftp
</pre>}}

=== OpenRC ===
{{RootCmd|rc-update add vsftpd default
|/etc/init.d/vsftpd start}}

=== systemd ===
{{RootCmd|systemctl enable vsftpd
|systemctl start vsftpd}}

